data.description: LAST CHANCE!  PRICE REDUCTION!  PRICE REDUCTION!! AGENTS BRING YOUR BEST OFFER!!Located in the THRIVING, HIGHLY DESIRED & EVER-GROWING City of Los Angeles. This is a home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, on a 5,096 Sq Ft lot, with direct alley access.  Very close to public transit and very close and easy access to the 105 and 110 freeways. Don't miss opportunity to make this well priced property your own, first-time buyer?  Perfect!! This beautiful home in the interior has large living room with fireplace for those cold cozy days with family, kitchen is very well maintained, 2 bathrooms has double sink each one, indoor laundry, the owner removed the carpet on bedrooms for convenience to feel the clean through the house. Front and back patios in a prime location, detached, with remote control garage for 2 cars, ensures your vehicles is well cared for and.. the whole house has a fence around it!  Owner already looking for replacement home. This beauty won't last!
